item.title: coco
item.description: Coco brings a new WC line from Brightside Chameleon’s Gambit into our project via Hendrix/Dante from Ramblin' Exotics! Hendrix is a great mix of two recent WC sires, Gambit and Bolt, and we are very excited to add his daughter to our breeding group. She has phenomenal coloring for a female and has been able to lay and bounce back easily thus far.

item.title: lokana
item.description: Lokana is the half-sister of Loko. They each have a 50% chance of bringing Kromatisk’s amazing ybbb into our project, but Lokana also has Landy x Hamy from her dam, Shirley’s side. Really can’t go wrong with the two possibilities here. We are very excited to see how she proves out over the years :).
